videos.description: Mikiah Herbert Harrigan drives to the basket and beats her defender on the layup to extend Tennessee's lead.
videos.headline: Harrigan makes tough layup for Lady Vols

videos.description: Jaime Nared forces a turnover and finishes with the lay-in to force a South Carolina timeout.
videos.headline: Lady Vols take momentum with steal and score

videos.description: Rennia Davis sinks a long 3-pointer as the clock expires, giving the Lady Vols a 29-point 3rd quarter and the lead vs. South Carolina.
videos.headline: Lady Vols cap off big 3rd quarter with Davis buzzer-beater

videos.description: Anastasia Hayes passes it to Mercedes Russell who gets the lay up adding to her double-double vs. South Carolina.
videos.headline: Hayes connects with Russell for layup

videos.description: Kortney Dunbar sinks a 3-pointer to extend the Lady Vols' lead late vs. No. 7 South Carolina.
videos.headline: Dunbar pumps up crowd with late 3-pointer
